text: Fereydoun Ghanbari (, born 23 September 1977, kermanshah, Iran) is an Iranian wrestler. He won Gold medal at the 2004 Asian Wrestling Championships. In 1997 he won the Gold medal at Junior World Freestyle Wrestling Championships in Helsinki. ==Sources== *Profile Category:Living people Category:Iranian male sport wrestlers Category:Sportspeople from Kermanshah Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
